"{\"uid\": \"dutchnews.nl-2024-07-olympics-to-clip-wings-of-klm-as-french-tourists-avoid-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Air France-KLM has issued a profits warning because holidaymakers are expected to avoid flying from Paris during this summer's Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\\u2013KLM\", \"score\": 0.9999965368905062, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Air France-KLM\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\\u2013KLM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\\u2013KLM\"}, {\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996650786, \"rank\": 3.349144031014475e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch-French flag carrier is anticipating a loss of between \\u20ac160 million and \\u20ac180 million between June and August as French travellers choose to delay their holidays or depart from other cities, or both.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999995652777706, \"rank\": 4.335796390235837e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"International markets show a significant avoidance of Paris,\\\" the company said ina press release on Monday.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 407, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996650786, \"rank\": 3.349144031014475e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Travel between the city and other destinations is also below the usual June-August average as residents in France seem to be postponing their holidays until after the Olympic Games or considering alternative travel plans.\\\"\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999999734996, \"rank\": 1.1912248832941756e-10, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The profits warning relates to Air France and its subsidiary Transavia France, indicating that KLM does not expect its Amsterdam-based operations to be seriously affected.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2231869268482934e-30, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transavia_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Transavia France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transavia_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transavia_France\"}, {\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KLM\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.983589273457752e-28, \"text\": \"KLM\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KLM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KLM\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French capital is hosting the Olympic Games between July 26 and August 11.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999995652777706, \"rank\": 4.335796390235837e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics will begin on August 28, but the airline does not expect passenger numbers to be affected.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could not provide the Dutch News service, and keep it free of charge, without the generous support of our readers.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9998553961989, \"rank\": 0.0001425002182134376, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your donations allow us to report on issues you tell us matter, and provide you with a summary of the most important Dutch news each day.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9998553961989, \"rank\": 0.0001425002182134376, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our thanks to everyone who donates regularly to Dutch News.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9998553961989, \"rank\": 0.0001425002182134376, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It costs money to produce our daily news service, our original features and daily newsletters, and we could not do it without you.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have not yet made a donation, or did so a while ago, you can do so via these links  The DutchNews.nl team  Please help us making DutchNews.nl a better read by taking part in a short survey.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": []}]}"